        <item>
            <title>【實試】SONY REON POCKET 5 穿戴式冷氣，香港售價 + 1.5 倍冷卻功率、更慳電</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/sony-reon-pocket-5-first-impression/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-reon-pocket-5-first-impression</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/sony-reon-pocket-5-first-impression/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 02:01:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[個人移動裝置]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[運動科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY REON POCKET 5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[便攜冷氣]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1230702</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>好快就到夏天，出門口都想涼浸浸，你就需要一個智能手提冷氣。今日 Sony 就正式發佈了 Reon Pocket 5 便攜冷氣。新機冷卻功率進一步升級，而且電池更加耐用，配合溫度感應自動調節功能，以及一向 Reon Pocket 都有，在冬天專用的發熱功能，這部新一代穿戴式便攜冷氣又真是幾吸引。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0008-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0008-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0008.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230729" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0077-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0077-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0077.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0023-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0023-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0023-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>冷卻功率為上代 1.5 倍、續航力為上代 1.8 倍</h2><p>SONY 官方公佈 REON POCKET 5 穿戴式便攜冷氣。簡單來説它是一個掛頸式裝置，其傳導片將冷感或熱力傳遞到背部近頸部的皮膚。在夏天戶外活動時，可給用戶冰涼感覺，適合長期在戶外活動的朋友。掛頸式裝置亦可令用戶的雙手可用來做其他事，例如照顧小朋友或寵物。</p><h2>評測影片</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_66507"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/90on4cbkJFA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0028-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0028-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0028.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230703" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/img_8919-672x580.jpg" alt="" width="672" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/img_8919-672x580.jpg 672w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/img_8919.jpg 1042w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 672px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲官方數據展示最新一代 REON POCKET 5 在佩戴 5 分鐘後，由於主機冷卻功率更強，身體表面溫度下降幅度更大</p><p>REON POCKET 5 具有上代 1.5 倍的冷卻功率，帶來更強吸熱性能，而且電池使用時間最多長達上代 1.8 倍，更適合更長時間戶外活動。unwire 記者水哥還有小編實際使用，發現冷氣機變冷的速度相當快，很快就能為用戶帶來清涼快感。傳導板的感覺就像一杯雪凍了的不鏽鋼杯杯面。上代清涼度分 1~4、4+ 級，而今代就新加入了 5、5+ 級清涼度，實際上都可感覺到今代 REON POCKET 5 金屬片的製冷效果更強。用戶可通過手機 App 調節清涼程度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230723" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0045-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0045-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0045.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><strong>官方公佈之使用時間</strong></p><p><strong>冷氣模式</strong></p><p>等級 1：約 17 小時</p><p>等級 2：約 12 小時</p><p>等級 3：約 10 小時</p><p>等級 4：約 7.5 小時</p><p>等級 5：約 4 小時</p><p>等級 5+：需要連接外部電源才可使用</p><p><strong>暖氣模式</strong></p><p>等級 1：約 8 小時</p><p>等級 2：約 6 小時</p><p>等級 3：約 5 小時</p><p>等級 4：約 4 小時</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230728" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0080-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0080-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0080.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230727" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0083-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0083-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0083.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲當你連接流動電源時，可選擇最新的「5+」製冷模式，這個模式可説是馬上製冷而且效能頗強</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230750" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/440018668_9924040392-1-694x396.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="396" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/440018668_9924040392-1-694x396.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/440018668_9924040392-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在 5 級冷卻效能時，機身上方的噪音也僅在可輕微聽到的範圍</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230732" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0086-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0086-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0086.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在開啟 5+ 急速製冷時，REON POCKET 就會發出較強噪音，但在戶外（特別在城市環境）使用時被車聲掩蓋也不太聽到</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230734" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0096-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0096-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0096.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在冷房或冬天時，可開暖氣模式，REON POCKET 馬上變暖蛋</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/sony-reon-pocket-5/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">SONY Reon Pocket 5  開箱評測影片，隨身冷氣</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>智能冷暖模式：結合主機、TAG 自動控制冷暖度</h2><p>而除了手動設定清涼度外，更可透過智能冷暖模式，從你的衣服內的熱度與周邊環境溫度，智能設定清涼度。REON POCKET 5 套裝跟來了 REON POCKET TAG 感應器，內置的感應器可傳送環境溫度、濕度到智能手機，配合 REON POCKET 在衣服裡面的溫度，自動設定最適合的清涼度。例如在室內環境中，室溫大約為攝氏 25 度身體表面溫度與衣服內溫度較低，此時智能冷暖模式會設置為「微」；在陰天的戶外環境中，智能模式可為你設置為「弱」。而在炎熱的戶外環境下再步行 10 分鐘，你的皮膚與衣服內的溫度會變得較高，REON POCKET 會自動調節到「強」製冷效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0035-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0035-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0035.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲REON POCKET TAG 感應器可令智能調節更加貼合當時溫度</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230735" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0037-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0037-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0037.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲REON POCKET TAG 可獨立使用或配合 REON POCKET 使用，在手機上可顯示更準確的溫度、濕度</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0007-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0007-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0007.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲SMART COOL WARM 智能冷暖模式可根據需要自動調節放冷、熱</p><p>智能冷暖模式更可在製冷、製熱功能間切換。例如你身處室內冷氣較強的環境，可自動調節到 WARM MODE 放熱模式，而當你走到戶外，可自動切換到 COOL MODE 為你製冷。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230724" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0047-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0047-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0047.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家也可開啟 SMART COOL 模式只讓它製冷</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230726" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0054-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0054-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0054.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230725" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0052-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0052-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0052.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲REON POCKET 獨立吹風模式，可以馬上輸出強風</p><h2>適合不同衣服、頸圍用家</h2><p>REON POCKET 5 將備有兩款排氣口護蓋，無論穿 T 裇或者領口較高的裇衫，都可令製冷／製熱後的排氣順利從衣服排出。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0057-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0057-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0057.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0072-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0072-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0072.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>專用頸帶內置有彈性機械管與金屬線框，可隨意扭曲令主機更能貼服你的頸部，防止你在戶外走動時移位。外表的矽橡膠套可保持佩戴時的舒適感。附隨的頸帶適合 34mm 至 46mm 頸圍的用家使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230731" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0073-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0073-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0073.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230730" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0064-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0064-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0064.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲用家可以扭曲頸帶以調節頸帶鬆緊度</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0027-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0027-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/unwire0027.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲頸圍更細的用家，可選購「REON POCKET 專用頸帶（小）」配件</p><h2>REON POCKET 5 產品系列售價與供應</h2><p>所有產品預售日期：2024 年 4 月 23 日</p><p>正式發售日期：2024 年 5 月 7 日</p><p>限時預購禮遇：購買 REON POCKET 5 套裝 ($1,499) 送 REON POCKET 專用機套（原價$180）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1230704" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/img_8929-694x368.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="368" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/img_8929-694x368.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/img_8929-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>REON POCKET 5 套裝（型號：RNPK-5T）：包括 REON POCKET 5, TAG, 專用頸帶、雙排氣口蓋套裝</p><p>售價：HK$1,499</p><p>REON POCKET TAG（型號：RNPT-1）</p><p>售價：HK$199</p><p>(可配合 REON POCKET 4, REON POCKET 5 兩代主機使用）</p><p>REON POCKET 專用機套（型號：RNPC-1）</p><p>售價：HK$180</p><p>REON POCKET 專用頸帶（型號：RNPB-N4）</p><p>售價：HK$149</p><p>REON POCKET 專用頸帶（小）（型號：RNPB-N4s）</p><p>售價：HK$149</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/sony-reon-pocket-5/unwire_podcast/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">SONY Reon Pocket 5  開箱評測影片，隨身冷氣</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/23/sony-reon-pocket-5-first-impression/life-tech/">【實試】SONY REON POCKET 5 穿戴式冷氣，香港售價 + 1.5 倍冷卻功率、更慳電</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
